column4: I've got a dvd that was sent to me (publicity shots for a website) about 400MB of photos,, but i put it in, and the auto mount fails, gives me an error popup, "Invalid mount option when attempting to mount the volume 'UDF Volume'."
what do i need to do here?? i've tried changing my /etc/fstab, it was udf, iso9600, i switched it to iso9600, udf  and to just auto, not working
